; name - name of sound
; props - single property of entity; conditional expressions can be used;
; environment - mask for environment preset name; conditional expressions can be used;
; cycle_time - time period for a new sound start
; distance_threshold - dont start a sound if location near than threshold to another already played sounds
; play_distance - distance from listener to sound center or sound area border where sounds can start;
; stop_distance - distance from listener to sound center or sound area border far sounds stops;
; limit - maximum played sounds
; no_avoid_silence - disable immediate speaker restarting after sound moved out by distance
; area - sound with area; multiple areas with same tag merged; all merged areas use single sound for playback;
; loop - loop playback of a sound
; radius - area sound circle radius
